{"tid":29900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳勝利稱中方堅持捍衛南海主權","createTime":"2016-12-09T01:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T02:27:34.000Z","uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef37ce57cd76b044751a64e53dc18c92a5a1caac","tid":29900,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:15:09.000Z","msg":"￼<br />\n<br />\n吳勝利稱中方堅持捍衛南海主權<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=203175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D203175&d=cBE4krt8N6%2Fd703qFEzAp0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=c8ca4e9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D203175&h=d66e9e03\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=203175</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】解放軍海軍司令員吳勝利表示，中國在南沙的島礁建設完全合情合理合法。<br />\n<br />\n吳勝利在解放軍海軍收復西南沙群島70周年紀念活動表示，南沙的島礁建設是在自己的領土開展，中國政府秉持主權屬我、擱置爭議、共同開發的原則，主張通過談判協商解決爭端、通過規則機制管控分歧以及透過互利合作實現共贏。<br />\n<br />\n吳勝利強調，為保障南海周邊國家的和平發展提出四點倡議，包括尊重歷史、維護穩定、增進互信以及深化合作，堅決反對區域外國家插手南海問題，及用航行和飛越自由做藉口，侵犯和挑釁他國主權，破壞南海穩定。中國在1946年恢復在西南沙群島行使主權。"},{"pid":"d3df7901928f73297cbdbfa50665d82619d1bc71","tid":29900,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:16:10.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"fb1312b0c53226337532e9a68b367fc7f85996c7","tid":29900,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:17:56.000Z","msg":"唔！勝利！"},{"pid":"8546a00333addabfd40d37c9be707d48200662c3","tid":29900,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:17:11.000Z","msg":"大陸佬啲名真係柒到死"},{"pid":"9309b2a6ea418511defe33f2a863048fccd98b91","tid":29900,"uid":39412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:27:34.000Z","msg":"唔勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n解放軍中如有廣東仔真係唔老黎到痴線"}]}